# Company-specific exclusion values — example file.
# Copy this file to excluded_values-company-specific.conf and replace the entries with domains
# specific to your organisation (corporate domains, subsidiaries, internal network suffixes).
# excluded_values-company-specific.conf is listed in .gitignore to avoid leaking org-specific data.
#
# One value per line to exclude completely (destination IP or hostname, lowercased when matched).
# Lines starting with # are comments.

# --- Corporate domains ---
# Replace with your organisation's corporate domain(s).
# example: corp.example.com

# --- Subsidiary domains ---
# Replace with domain names belonging to your organisation's subsidiaries.
# example: subsidiary.example.com

# --- Internal network suffixes ---
# Replace with internal DNS suffixes used in your environment (non-routable / split-horizon DNS).
# example: internal.example
# example: corp.local
